  • Constructor Details

    • Parameter

      public Parameter(String lineFromFile) throws Exception
      Load the per month parameters from the appropriate line in the input file. Fragile. Parameters must be in the correct order.
      Parameters:
      lineFromFile - Array containing parameters IN THE CORRECT ORDER
      Throws:
      Exception - If any of the required parameters are missing or not numbers.
